<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body background="#F8F9FA">
    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <h1 class="text-primary text-uppercase">Car rent</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="container-xxl">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center" class="row justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <div class="p-3 bg-white col-6">
                <h3 class="text-secondary ">
                    Your
                    <b>Car Rent</b>
                    order information
                </h3>
                <p>Hi {{user.username}},</p>
                <p>Thank you for choosing our service, hope you enjoy that!</p>
                <div class="mt-4">
                    <p>
                        <b>ID:</b>
                        {{order.id}}
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <b>Order name:</b>
                        {{order.orderName}}
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <b>Address:</b>
                        {{order.orderAddress}}
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <b>Phone number:</b>
                        {{order.orderPhoneNumber}}
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <b>City:</b>
                        {{order.orderCity}}
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <b>Price:</b>
                        {{order.totalPrice}}
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <b>Status:</b>
                        {{order.status}}
                    </p>
                    <div class="ps-4">
                        <p>
                            <b>Details:</b>
                        </p>
                        <span class="fw-bold">Car:</span>
                        <div class="row flex-column">
                            <img class="col-6" style="width: 200px; height: 100px;" src={{orderDetail.car.thumbnailUrl}}
                                alt=""><br>
                            <p class="col-6">{{orderDetail.car.languages.0.carName}}</p>
                        </div>
                        <span> <b>Type: </b> {{orderDetail.car.carTypes.0.carType.languages.0.carTypeName}}</span><br>
                        <span> <b>Pick up city:</b> {{orderDetail.pickUpCity.name}}</span><br>
                        <span> <b>Drop off city:</b> {{orderDetail.dropOffCity.name}}</span><br>
                        <span> <b>Pick up at:</b> {{orderDetail.pickUpAt}}</span><br>
                        <span> <b>Drop off at:</b> {{orderDetail.dropOffAt}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-3">
                    <p>If you have any question, send us a note at</p>
                    <p>Cheers,</p>
                    <p>The team at Car rent</p>
                </div>
            </div>
</body>

</html>